## API Endpoints

- `GET /` - API information
- `GET /health` - Health check
- `GET /api/schedule` - View posting schedule
- `POST /api/trigger-post` - Manual post trigger
- `POST /api/create-post` - Create custom post
- `GET /docs` - Interactive API documentation

